short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Collaborate, conclude, contribute with 9mCollab for Chrome.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
9M Inc is on a mission to empower people to lead more productive communication with  less noise and distraction, less inconclusive discussions and to make the right decisions faster.

With 9mCollab you will enjoy well structured, distraction free communication, that is seamlessly transferred into knowledge base through a highly efficient conclusions driven process.

Collaborate - Enjoy distraction free collaboration.

Conclude - Reach conclusions and make decisions fast.

Contribute - Create internal knowledge base via shared conclusions.
